summary: An Ordinance accepting a quit-claim deed from George A. Moomaw, and Francis C. Moomaw, his wife and John M. Anderson and Anna Anderson, his wife, to the City of Ballard, dated the 1st day of September, 1903 to all of Lots One (1) to Thirty-three (33) inclusive and Lots Thirty-five (35) to Forty-eight (48) inclusive all in Block six (6) Ballard Water Front Addition to the City of Ballard.
